<subSubSection box="[1445,2182,1024,1057]" pageId="46" pageNumber="530" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="46.[1445,2654,275,1337]" box="[1445,2182,1024,1057]" pageId="46" pageNumber="530">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1445,1681,1024,1057]" pageId="46" pageNumber="530">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Western Nectar Bats are nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
